romancer who transgresses the boundary between life and death... Every cycle is an ending, and every death is a new beginning. Explore, fight, light the flames, and search for the fragments of dawn among countless distortions and madness.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You'll face the abyss and hear its whispers.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You'll burn yourself and become the eternal fire.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">And when you stand at the end of the broken time, facing the indescribable being, you must make your own choice.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">To be its continuation, or to destroy its heart...</p>","developers":["insight studio"],"fullgame":{"appid":"3419290","name":"GOD FORSAKEN"},"genres":[{"description":"Action","id":"1"},{"description":"Indie","id":"23"},{"description":"RPG","id":"3"}],"header_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3476690/header.jpg?t=1739504924","is_free":true,"linux_requirements":[],"mac_requirements":[],"movies":[{"highlight":true,"id":257091464,"mp4":{"480":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257091464/movie480.mp4?t=1739348773","max":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257091464/movie_max.mp4?t=1739348773"},"name":"\u5ba3\u4f20\u5b9e\u673a","thumbnail":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/257091464/db1c2bdf6d2d83fb0c40fe787d6048b8cb53e091/movie_600x337.jpg?t=1739348773","webm":{"480":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257091464/movie480_vp9.webm?t=1739348773","max":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257091464/movie_max_vp9.webm?t=1739348773"}},{"highlight":true,"id":257091463,"mp4":{"480":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257091463/movie480.mp4?t=1739348776","max":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257091463/movie_max.mp4?t=1739348776"},"na